  <brief_title>Splinting Versus Casting for Type I Supracondylar Fractures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Splinting Versus Above Elbow Casting for Type I Supracondylar Fractures of the Humerus in Children: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
